-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

nmap:  Network mapper or Network scanner.
Commands:
    - `nmap -F www.netflix.com` : scans netflix.com for all the ports. 'F' flag is used for faster scanning
    - `nmap -p 20-25,80,443 -F www.netflix.com` : Scans for port 20 to 25, 80 and 443 for netflix
    - `nmap -A www.netflix.com` : Aggressive scan. It also displays traceroute i.e. route taken by a packet from source to destination
    - `nmap --traceroute www.netflix.com` : traceroute for netflix
    - `nmap -V www.netflix.com` : version of the service
    - `nmap -o www.netflix.com` : OS for the host
    - `nmap -F -oN output.txt www.netflix.com` : save the result in output.txt

